title: Drone captures last moments of Lashkar terrorists killed in Pulwama encounter | Jammu and Kashmir
description: A drone camera of security forces has captured the last moments of three Lashkar-e-Taiba militants killed in an encounter yesterday in Pulwama district of south Kashmir. The footage shows three Lashkar militants positioning themselves outside a residential house to take on security personnel who had cornered them from all sides. All the three militants, which include a 9-day old teen recruit from Srinagar, were shot dead in a brief firefight. Watch the video for more details.|#Kashmir #Pulwama #Lashkar #LeT #Drone #terrorists #IndianArmy #Srinagar #JammuKashmir #Pakistan #militancy #insurgency

title: Jokowi dan Anies Tinjau Lokasi Formula E: Awal Juni Lihat Balapannya
description: JAKARTA, KOMPAS.TV   - Presiden Joko Widodo bersama Gubernur DKI Jakarta Anies Baswedan telah meninjau lokasi Formula E, pada Senin (25/4/2202). ||||Pada kesempatan itu Presiden Jokowi menjawab sejumlah pertanyaan awak media terkait persiapan pelaksanaan Formula E. ||||"Saya ingin melihat persiapan formula E seperti apa di lapangan. Kita lihat untuk trek balapannya sudah siap tinggal dikejar pemasangan paddock, grandstand, pagar, masih ada waktu abis lebaran. Kita harapkan awal Juni melihat balapannya,"ucap Jokowi. ||||Baca Juga Didampingi Anies, Jokowi Tinjau Pembangunan Sirkuit Formula E di https://www.kompas.tv/article/283234/didampingi-anies-jokowi-tinjau-pembangunan-sirkuit-formula-e||||Kemudian Anies pun menjelaskan untuk trek balapan sudah siap 100 persen. ||||"Izin pak presiden, kalau untuk trek 100 persen, dalam proses pembangunan paddock, grandstand, dan pagar, nanti di pagar beton ada pagar untuk pelindung. Itu semua lagi dikerjakan, fasilitas tamu-tamu, Secara umu treknya sudah 100 persen,"jelas Anies pada media.||||Lebih lanjut Formula E akan digelar di Ancol, Jakarta Utara pada Juni mendatang tepatnya pada pada 4 Juni 2022.||||Video Editor: Vila Randita|| ||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/283247/jokowi-dan-anies-tinjau-lokasi-formula-e-awal-juni-lihat-balapannya

title: Marcon defeats far-right rival Le Pen; Vows to unite France after bagging 2nd term
description: French President Emmanuel Macron defeated far-right rival Marine Le Pen by a comfortable margin. Macron secured a second term, heading off what would have been a political earthquake. Cheers of joy erupted as results appeared on a screen at the Champ de Mars park at the foot of the Eiffel tower. Supporters waved French & EU flags - people hugged each other, danced and chanted 'Macron!'. Le Pen, who at one stage trailed Macron by a few points in opinion polls, quickly admitted defeat. However, Le Pen vowed to keep up the fight, with parliamentary elections looming in June. Watch the full video for more.|#EmmanuelMacron #MarineLePen #France #Macron

title: Hari Pertama Uji Coba Ganjil Genap di Tol Cikampek, Antisipasi Macet Selama Arus Mudik Lebaran 2022
description: KARAWANG, KOMPAS.TV - Uji coba ganjil genap tol telah dilakukan pada pukul 11.00 WIB hari ini, Senin 25 April 2022.||||Dimulai dari gerbang Tol Cikampek Utama kilometer 47.||||Baca Juga Uji Coba Ganjil Genap Tol Cikampek, Jasa Marga Siagakan Petugas hingga Pemasangan Rambu di https://www.kompas.tv/article/282984/uji-coba-ganjil-genap-tol-cikampek-jasa-marga-siagakan-petugas-hingga-pemasangan-rambu||||Uji coba ganjil genap dilakukan selama tiga hari, dengan tujuan untuk mengurai kemacetan selama arus mudik lebaran 2022.||||Data dari Kementerian Perhubungan, bakal ada 85 juta pemudik, tahun ini dengan 47 persennya, yakni sekitar 40 juta orang menggunakan jalur darat.||||Baca Juga Warga Mulai PadatI Hotel Jelang Puncak Mudik Tiba, Pengusaha Hotel Mulai Dapat Angin Segar di https://www.kompas.tv/article/283123/warga-mulai-padati-hotel-jelang-puncak-mudik-tiba-pengusaha-hotel-mulai-dapat-angin-segar||||Karena itu, uji coba aturan ganjil genap diberlakukan. ||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/283126/hari-pertama-uji-coba-ganjil-genap-di-tol-cikampek-antisipasi-macet-selama-arus-mudik-lebaran-2022

title: WW2 Guns Still Used in Today's Ukraine war
description: For centuries wars are being fought with contemporary weapons and in some instances with  future or prototype ones. However some old weapons, older than their current users, are being utilized. The Ukraine war has shown that some very old designs can still be used. Machine guns from a century ago, bolt action rifles older than that, submachine guns designed for WW2, anti-tank rifles as relics of the same conflict are being used, in big numbers or some rare occasions.|ï»¿Each of these weapons   tell  us a story and serve as a testament of durability and the overall change and shift in the military doctrine as well as the consequences of the current situation. Not only that but those weapons, very crude and old, are serving on par with the latest designs, making the situation even more peculiar.|ï»¿Most of those weapons have survived the harsh conditions of the biggest conflict in human history, years of storage and later wars beyond that. Some were served for decades as  museum exhibits only to be called once again to fight in today's wars.|Become a Simple History member: https://www.youtube.com/simplehistory/join|Support us on Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/simplehistory|Copyright: DO NOT translate and re-upload our content on Youtube or other social media.|SIMPLE HISTORY MERCHANDISE |Get the Simple History books on Amazon: |https://www.amazon.com/Daniel-Turner-%60/e/B00H5TYLAE/|T-Shirts|https://teespring.com/stores/simple-history-official-merch|Simple history gives you the facts, simple!|See the book collection here:|Amazon USA|http://www.amazon.com/Daniel-Turner/e/B00H5TYLAE/|Amazon UK|http://www.amazon.co.uk/Daniel-Turner/e/B00H5TYLAE/|https://www.facebook.com/Simple-History-549437675141192/|https://twitter.com/SimpleHistoryYT|Credit:|Created by Daniel Turner (B.A. (Hons) in History, University College London) |Script and animation Aleksandar Djokic|Narrator:|Chris Kane|https://vocalforge.com/

description: Undercover in Nederland is te zien bij SBS6. |Bekijk alle afleveringen op KIJK.nl: https://bit.ly/3ybdUEB|ABONNEER op SBS6 voor meer video's: http://bit.ly/2qiTx8c|VOLG SBS6 op social media! |Facebook | SBS6|TikTok | SBS6nl|Instagram | SBS6NL|OVER Undercover in Nederland...|Het is inmiddels een vertrouwd straatbeeld: pakketbezorgers en medewerkers van bezorgdiensten zoals Thuisbezorgd, staan dagelijks voor de deur. Overvallers weten dat ook en maken daar op een vreselijke manier misbruik van. De afgelopen tijd kwam het ene na het andere nieuwsbericht over deze zorgwekkende trend naar buiten. Bekende en onbekende Nederlanders worden op verschrikkelijke wijze overvallen in hun eigen huis. In deze uitzending van Undercover in Nederland duiken Alberto Stegeman en zijn team in de schimmige wereld van de handel in uniformen, die door criminelen worden gebruikt voor brute overvallen en inbraken. Gewapend met verborgen camera's starten zij een onderzoek naar deze dubieuze handel. Het gaat om kleding van bezorgdiensten, maar ook politiekleding wordt online aangeboden. Er zijn meerdere confrontaties met de aanbieders en als een louche dealer politiekleding aanbiedt en Alberto hem wil confronteren, is ook de politie zelf niet ver uit de buurt.

Hay varios mecanismos que favorecen este retorno.|1:06 Â¿CÃ“MO SE PRODUCE EL RETORNO VENOSO?|En primer lugar la planta del pie, es como una esponja, al poner peso sobre el pie o mover los dedos de los pies conseguimos que esa red de venas se vacÃ­e, como si estuviÃ©ramos apretando una esponja.|AdemÃ¡s la contracciÃ³n muscular, especÃ­ficamente la contracciÃ³n del gemelo, al que denominamos segundo corazÃ³n, es el mecanismo estrella a la hora de bombear la sangre de las piernas hasta el torso.|El diafragma en la respiraciÃ³n produce un efecto de vacÃ­o en el abdomen, y el propio corazÃ³n tiene un efecto de aspiraciÃ³n que favorece el retorno aunque bien mucho menos importante que cuando propulsa la sangre venosa.|AdemÃ¡s de todo esto, las venas tienen un sistema de vÃ¡lvulas que permite el movimiento de la sangre venosa en una sola direcciÃ³n, como cuando se infla un flotador en la playa, la sangre venosa sube cerrÃ¡ndose la vÃ¡lvula detrÃ¡s impidiendo que la sangre vuelva a bajar.|4:14 ACTIVIDAD DEPORTIVA|El primer consejo es llevar a cabo actividad fÃ­sica de forma regular. Pero, no cualquier actividad fÃ­sica, la OMS recomienda completar al menos 150 minutos de actividad de moderada a vigorosa a la semana, para mantener una buena salud mental y cardiovascular.|Si cuando realizas una actividad deportiva, eres capaz de mantener una conversaciÃ³n tranquilamente, estÃ¡s llevando a cabo una actividad de intensidad baja.|Si por el contrario cuando haces deporte puedes mantener una conversaciÃ³n pero notas que te falta el aire, entonces estÃ¡s llevando a cabo una actividad de intensidad moderada.|Si por Ãºltimo no puedes mantener una conversaciÃ³n cuando llevas a cabo tu actividad deportiva se trata, sin lugar a dudas de una actividad vigorosa.|6:00 EVITAR EL SEDENTARISMO|Si te falta tiempo y no puedes hacer deporte durante la semana, intenta moverte todo lo posible, evita permanecer largos periodos de tiempo sentado o inmÃ³vil. El efecto del calor y el frÃ­o sobre las arterias y las venas es vasodilatador y vasoconstrictor provocando una especie de contracciÃ³n en los vasos sanguÃ­neos. |8:31 ROPA AJUSTADA SOBRE TODO EN GEMELO E INGLE|Evitar el uso de ropa ajustada, sobre todo en la zona de los gemelos y la ingle, y limitar el uso de talones puede ser tambiÃ©n Ãºtil. title: I'm ADDICTED to my Porsche Taycan 4S Cross Turismo! - 9000 Mile Full Review
description: Install Raid for FreeÂ âœ…Â IOS/ANDROID/PC: https://clcr.me/D6yFNL and get a special starter packÂ ğŸ’¥Â Available only for the next 30 days|Welcome back to RBR guys & this is my own #Porsche Taycan Cross Turismo. Last time I drove it on the channel it was the German Press car Cross Turismo Turbo S that top gear had half destroyed off roading it. And what a car it was! The aggressive super wagon looks rivalled even the RS6, and the massive speed and practicality won us all over, so much so that I bought one and you guys viewed the video almost a million times.|As of today Iâ€™ve done over 9000(!?) miles in my 4S, in mere months as my combustion cars lay gathering dust.|Why have I been so addicted to it? What makes it better than my other daily #supercars? What did I love and what did I hate? These are some off the questions Iâ€™ll answer in todays review and report on living with my first #EV from Porsche, so letâ€™s get to it and review my cross Turismo 4S!|So as a reminder - the two-tier Performance Battery Plus used in the Taycan Turbo S comes as standard in the CT, itâ€™s just under 100kw size and it can charge from 20% to 80% in 20 minutes!|At home I use the CTEK Home Charger, as seen in the video:|https://www.ctek.com/uk/ev-charging/chargestormÂ®-connected-910-17028|The electric motors used are Permanent magnet synchronous electric motors, or PSM. These are always alive and give much higher output without overheating vs systems used in past Teslas. The 4S has a 600-amp pulse inverter which is our motor on the rear, and a 300 AMP inverter on the front too; and of course the 2 speed gearbox, 1st gear is mainly used in Sport or Sport Plus modes.|Technical Changes Vs  the standard Taycan include a more off road and yet more compliant suspension, using a three-chamber air set up giving a wide range of spring rates & heights. The rear is way larger, we have 47 mm more headroom and a boot with 40 litres more and the all important hatchback - Iâ€™ll give you some storage tips on this.|The more important thing is perfoance however, here the 4S Cross Turismo has  490HP on the road and then overboost and Launch Control of 571. They say acceleration 0-60 is 4.1 secondsâ€¦ this is a bald faced lie! Wait to see the launch info here.|Having done 9000 miles, Iâ€™m gonna focus on my experience with this car as my first electric vehicle. That means telling you guys all the things I discovered, things I loved, things that really irritated me, and in general why Iâ€™m sold on the Taycan as a product.|As an example, PCM in Taycan crashes with black screens a lot, so I give you a Debug screen fix to help owners. I discover how Lift mode is really useful, how to clean the rear camera which was not obvious (neither way vent control inside) and find an amazing dynamic ambient light option!|The main point I wanna put across, is how I feel living with this versus something like an E 63 or the M5 - which is where I see this car fitting! title: India's payback for Beijing not allowing Indian students' return? Chinese tourist visas suspended
description: India has suspended tourist visas issued to Chinese nationals, global airlines body IATA told its member carriers on April 20. India has been raising with China the plight of approximately 22,000 Indian students enrolled in Chinese universities who are unable to go back for physical classes. However, the neighbouring country has till date refused to let them enter. These students had to leave their studies in China and come to India when the COVID-19 pandemic began in the beginning of 2020. Watch this video for more. |#India #China #Travel #Visa #PMModi #Xijinping #Tourist  #Students

title: Can the global criminal network be destroyed? | DW Documentary
description: Organized crime can hold sway over political and economic institutions. Illegal business is growing more profitable every day. Can something be done to take down this global criminal network?|Corruption and drug trafficking are no longer just local problems. International groups working with terrorist organizations and politicians are ruthlessly spreading violence and endangering innocent lives. Complex infrastructures enable them to evade capture and punishment.  |Drug smuggling is a competitive global business. Drug smugglers transport their goods from Latin America to Europe. From international money laundering to transnational murder for hire, we see the devastation underground business leaves in its wake. Murders, explosions, and targeted attacks - they affect not only criminals, but also their families, witnesses, journalists, and other innocent victims. |According to FBI and Europol documents, every country on earth now has its own criminal groups and cartels. They are also gaining a stronger footing in Germany. Take drug trafficking, for example: Germany is a well-organized market and central transport hub for opiates along the Balkan route. South America directly serves the U.S. market. Anyone attempting to expose these groups is placing her or his life on the line.  |According figures from the World Bank, organized crime groups spend half of their annual two trillion dollar annual profits bribing politicians across the globe. Those operating with full cooperation from the authorities are behaving more like terror organizations: They use fear and terror, murder and manslaughter. But using the global financial system for money laundering is nothing new.  The state earns money through taxes and terror groups get rich in the process.|Drugs and money are not the only things being transported. Smuggling people has also become a lucrative business for organized crime, bringing in about $150 billion each year. |Could conditions like those in Russia develop elsewhere, where politicians, secret services and criminals share common interests? Could this even happen in once stable democracies like the USA or core European states? Is there a way out? Or are law enforcement agencies powerless to stop them?|#documentary #dwdocumentary |______|DW Documentary gives you knowledge beyond the headlines. title: 15 Heroes Spider-Man Could Team Up With Next
description: The friendly neighborhood webhead has an interesting future ahead of him in the MCU. After the heartbreaking conclusion to Spider-Man: No Way Home that left Peter Parker not only with his Aunt May gone, but also basically with his identity erased, it has set the stage for the young hero to be a little more independent in his next adventure. But as fun as it is watching solo Spider-Man movies, itâ€™s also a blast seeing Peter Parker team up with other heroes! Heâ€™s so fun to watch when he has another Avenger to bounce off of and I think a team up movie could be a lot of fun in the future! But who would he work with best?|I think the logical choice would be Daredevil. The two have already interacted a little bit in the MCU, and having Spider-Man team up with the Man Without Fear would be an interesting way to further Peterâ€™s personal journey. Heâ€™s used to fighting huge, world-ending threats now, so how would Peter function against a crime boss like Kingpin? Heâ€™d have to adopt a totally different set of skills! Or what about a new hero like Yelena? She could show Peter a grittier side of what it takes to be a hero in a street-level type of adventure! Or instead of street-level, would you have Peter go back to the cosmic side of things and team up with the Guardians of the Galaxy? Thereâ€™s a lot of options!|So join me today as I break down all the different heroes Spidey could team up with in the future. After  youâ€™re done, be sure to hit that big like and subscribe button for more awesome MCU content like this! And go ahead and leave a comment while youâ€™re at it! Thanks for watching CBR! title: PM Modi's first visit to J&K after Art 370 purge. He has this message for Kashmiri youth
description: Prime Minister Narendra Modi assured Kashmiri youth on Sunday that he won't let them suffer like their parents and grandparents and will work towards making their life better and prosperous. PM Modi addressed a huge gathering in Jammu today and it was his first visit to J&K after his government stripped the erstwhile state of its special status and statehood. PM Modi also lauded the fact that all Indian laws are now applicable in Jammu and Kashmir and that all J&K residents are equal citizens of India. Watch the video for more.|#JammuKashmir #Jammu #Kashmir  #Article370 #NarendraModi #BJP #PMModi #Pakistan #India

title: Jammu man makes PM Modi's six-foot statue in record time; Gets praise from the Prime Minister
description: Prime Minister Narendra Modi met a renowned sculptor from Jammu named Ravinder Jamwal  who made a 6-foot-tall statue of Prime Minister. PM Modi took the time out to meet the sculptor and laud him for the statue effort. PM Modi was in J&K for the first time since abrogation of article 370. PM Modi and J&K Lt governor Manoj Sinha posed for a picture with the sculptor and his wife. Watch this video for more.|#Jammu #PMModi #J&K #RavinderJamwal #ModiStatue #India #Viral #Trending #Video

title: Banihal-Qazigund Road Tunnel: Strengthening Connectivity, Boosting Tourism
description: Prime Minister inaugurated the Banihal-Qazigund Road Tunnel. The 8.45 Km long tunnel would reduce the road distance between Banihal and Qazigund by 16 km, and reduce journey time by around one and a half hour. It is a twin tube tunnel â€“ one for each direction of travel â€“ with the twin tubes being interconnected by a cross passage every 500m, for maintenance and emergency evacuation. title: How are Ukrainian children escaping the Russian invasion settling in the UK? â€“ BBC News
description: It's now thought that more than 10 million people, including two million children, have had to leave their homes in Ukraine since Russia invaded the country at the end of February.|Ukrainians have been trying to find safety in neighbouring countries such as Poland and Moldova, as well as travelling further to countries such as Germany and the UK.|15-year-old Polina, her five-year-old sister, Taisiia, and their mum, Svetlana, have made a journey from Ukraine to the UK to find a new life.|Please subscribe HERE http://bit.ly/1rbfUog|#Ukraine #Russia #BBCNews

title: Ukrainians, Russians mark Orthodox Easter in time of war | DW News
description: Ukraine's President Volodymyr Zelenskyy visited Kyiv's St. Sofia Cathedral to record an Easter message on the holiest day of the Orthodox Christian calendar. At makeshift prayer venues and churches around the country, Ukrainians prayed for those fighting on the front lines, and for those trapped in places like the besieged city of Mariupol. DW Correspondent Rebecca Ritters visited one village north east of Kyiv that was under Russian control until a few weeks ago. The community there came together to build a makeshift chapel after Russian soldiers destroyed their church.|Like Ukraine, Russia is also a predominantly Orthodox country. President Vladimir Putin attended an Easter mass early on Sunday in Moscow's Christ the Savior Cathedral. |The service was led by the head of the Russian Orthodox Church Patriach Kirill, who said he hoped the conflict in Ukraine would end quickly. Kirill has strongly backed the Kremlin's war in Ukraine. description: ------------------- #MenangBersama -------------------------|Dapatkan kabar terbaru tentang jadwal pertandingan, kondisi tim terbaru dan segala pernik terkait PERSIB di laman resmi PERSIB: http://persib.co.id|Unduh pula aplikasi PERSIBapp sebagi pintu utama untuk lebih dekat dengan PERSIB: http://onelink.to/persibapp|Subscribe Kanal YouTube resmi PERSIB https://www.youtube.com/user/PersibOfficial?sub_confirmation=1|Ikuti kami di:|Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/PERSIB-Bandung-21164211233/|Twitter: https://twitter.com/persib|Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/persib|Line @persibbandung: https://line.me/R/ti/p/%40persibbandung|..-..|Ini adalah kanal YouTube resmi dari PERSIB, klub terbesar di Indonesia dan Asia yang berasal dari Bandung. title: Ketum IDI Temui Panglima TNI Andhika Perkasa, Bahas Soal Terawan?
description: JAKARTA, KOMPAS.TV  Ketua Umum Ikatan Dokter Indonesia (IDI) dan Jajaran Pengurus bertemu dengan Panglima TNI Jenderal Andika Perkasa.||||Hal ini diunggah di kanal Youtube Jenderal TNI Andika Perkasa pada Minggu (24/4)||||Dalam kesempatan itu, Ketua Umum IDI Adib Hidayat memperkenalkan pengurus baru IDI Hasil Muktamar Aceh.||||Dalam kesempatan itu, Ketum IDI juga membahas megnenai keputusan pemberhentian tetap Terawan dari keanggotaan IDI.||||Adib menjelaskan basih memberi ruang kepada terawan untuk menjadi Anggota kembali.||||"Pemberhentian tetap itu tidak diartikan seumur hidup. Jadi masih ada upaya ruang kalau kami sampaikan masih ada ruang kalau beliau berkenan untuk menjadi anggota kembali kita akan kuatkan forum secara internal," ucap Adib.||||Tanggapi hal tersebut, Panglima TNI Andika Perkasa bertanya mengenai pengaruh keputusan pemberhentian Terawan dari IDI dan Izin prakteknya di RSPAD Gatot Subroto.||||"Apa yang berpengaruh terhadap izin praktek Dokter Terawan di RSPAD kalau keanggotaan beliau tidak lagi aktif tetapi sebagai dokter yang juga praktek di rumah sakit kami? Itu juga kita akan ikut aturan," tanya Andika.||||Video Editor: Faqih Fisabilillah||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/282954/ketum-idi-temui-panglima-tni-andhika-perkasa-bahas-soal-terawan

title: Momen Presiden Rusia Putin Hadiri Misa Paskah Ortodoks di Moskow Rusia
description: MOSKOW, KOMPAS.TV  Inilah momen saat Presiden Rusia Vladimir Putin menghadiri kebaktian Paskah Ortodoks di Moskow pada Sabtu (23/4) malam.||||Tampak Putin juga didampingi Walikota Moskow Sergey Sobyanin memegangi lilin merah yang menyala||||Baca Juga Zelensky Mengaku Khawatir Putin Hilang Akal dan Nekat Bom Nuklir Ukraina di https://www.kompas.tv/article/282837/zelensky-mengaku-khawatir-putin-hilang-akal-dan-nekat-bom-nuklir-ukraina||||Kepala Gereja Ortodoks Rusia, Patriark Kirill, memimpin kebaktian di Katedral Kristus Sang Juru Selamat Moskow.||||Pada perayaan luar ruangan Paskah Ortodox yang digelar di Moskwa pada Sabtu (23/4/2022), Kirill mengatakan dia berharap konflik di Ukraina akan berakhir dengan cepat tetapi tidak mengutuknya.||||Video Editor: Faqih Fisabilillah||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/282925/momen-presiden-rusia-putin-hadiri-misa-paskah-ortodoks-di-moskow-rusia

description: JAKARTA, KOMPAS.TV - Hanya berselang tiga hari, setelah Dirjen Perdagangan Luar Negeri, Indrasari Wisnu Wardhana, dan tiga bos perusahaan minyak swasta ditetapkan sebagai tersangka kasus dugaan tindakan melawan hukum atas pemberian izin ekspor minyak goreng, pemerintah bereaksi.||||Presiden melarang ekspor sawit dan minyak goreng, mulai 28 April 2022, agar stok minyak goreng di dalam negeri melimpah, dengan harapan harganya perlahan turun.||||Namun, menanggapi larangan ini, Gabungan Pengusaha Kelapa Sawit Indonesia, atau GAPKI, meminta pemerintah untuk mengevaluasi kebijakan ini.||||Baca Juga Soroti Kasus Korupsi Minyak Goreng, AHY: Usut Tuntas, Jangan Sampai Ada Kambing Hitam! di https://www.kompas.tv/article/282891/soroti-kasus-korupsi-minyak-goreng-ahy-usut-tuntas-jangan-sampai-ada-kambing-hitam||||Komisi Pengawas Persaingan Usaha, KPPU, sebelumnya telah mengendus indikasi praktik kartel, di antara para pengusaha minyak goreng.||||Namun, struktur pasar oligopoli yang tak sehat, seakan membuat pemerintah tak punya pilihan.||||Organisasi Kelompok Sawit Watch menilai, kebijakan presiden melarang ekspor minyak sawit mentah, dan minyak goreng, tak bisa serta merta menurunkan harga.||||Masalah utama justru berada di kebijakan pemerintah, yang tak kunjung membenahi struktur pasar minyak goreng, yang tak sehat.||||Tak hanya bisa diakali dengan perubahan strategi produksi oleh para produsen, kebijakan larangan ekspor minyak goreng, juga dikhawatirkan, bisa memicu kebijakan balasan dari luar negeri, yang bergantung pada pasokan minyak sawit mentah Indonesia.||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/282923/kebijakan-presiden-larang-ekspor-minyak-disebut-tak-akan-turunkan-harga-minyak-goreng

title: Bupati Sukoharjo Geram Tembok Benteng Keraton Kartasura Dijebol
description: SUKOHARJO, KOMPAS.TV - Dijebolnya tembok yang berstatus obyek dalam kajian benda cagar budaya di petilasan Keraton Kartasura, Sukoharjo, Jawa Tengah Membuat Bupati Sukoharjo Etik Suryani marah-marah kepada pelaku perusakan.||||Etik mendatangi langsung TKP pada Sabtu (23/4) siang tadi untuk melihat secara langsung untuk berhadapan dengan pembeli tanah tersebut.||||Saat berdialog, bupati sangat menyayangkan kenapa penjebolan tembok ini bisa terjadi||||Baca Juga Fakta-Fakta Yulianto, Jagal Kartasura Pembantai 7 Orang Termasuk Anggota Kopassus yang Dihukum Mati di https://www.kompas.tv/article/165224/fakta-fakta-yulianto-jagal-kartasura-pembantai-7-orang-termasuk-anggota-kopassus-yang-dihukum-mati||||Dirinya menyerahkan kasus ini untuk ditangani pihak yang berwenang.||||Bupati juga berharap dinas pendidikan dan kebudayaan melakukan inventarisir semua situs yang ada di Sukoharjo.||||Terjadinya penjebolan tembok ini karena tanah yang sudah dibeli dan dirinya mengaku tidak tahu kalau tembok ini masuk obyek dalam kajian benda cagar budaya.||||Video Editor: Faqih Fisabilillah||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/282872/bupati-sukoharjo-geram-tembok-benteng-keraton-kartasura-dijebol

title: Jalur Pantura Semakin Padat Pemudik! Arteri Karawang hingga Cirebon Didominasi Kendaraan Roda Empat
description: KOMPAS.TV - Arus mudik di Jalur Pantura Jawa semakin padat.||||Sabtu (23/4) malam, Jalur Arteri Karawang menuju Pantura Cirebon maupun Jawa Tengah dipadati kendaraan pemudik yang memilih perjalanan malam.||||Pemudik roda dua maupun roda empat mulai memadati Jalur Arteri Karawang menuju Cirebon, Jawa Tengah hingga Jawa Timur.||||Perjalanan malam banyak dipilih pemudik untuk perjalanan pulang kampung karena pertimbangan cuaca yang lebih sejuk dan perjalanan cenderung lebih lancar dibandingkan pada siang hari.||||Berdasarkan pantauan Kompas TV, gelombang arus mudik mengalami peningkatan sejak Jumat (22/4) malam dan terus terjadi hingga Sabtu (23/4) malam.||||Meski demikian, arus lalu lintas masih terpantau lancar.||||Sementara itu, peningkatan arus kendaraan pemudik juga terlihat di Gerbang Tol Palimanan, Cirebon, Jawa Barat, pada Sabtu (23/4) malam.||||Kendaraan berpelat luar daerah tampak ramai bergerak dari arah Jakarta menuju Jawa Tengah dan Jawa Timur.||||Sebagian kendaraan bahkan memenuhi bagian atap mobil dengan barang-barang untuk dibawa ke kampung halaman.||||Pihak pengelola tol mencoba meniadakan transaksi pembayaran di Gerbang Tol Palimanan untuk memperlancar laju kendaraan.||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/282862/jalur-pantura-semakin-padat-pemudik-arteri-karawang-hingga-cirebon-didominasi-kendaraan-roda-empat

title: RARA MUTTON CURRY | RARA GOSHT | MUTTON RARA | MUTTON RARA GOSHT
description: Rara Mutton Curry | Rara Gosht | Mutton Rara Recipe | Mutton Rara Gosht | How To Make Rara Mutton | Keema Mutton Masala | Rara Mutton | Rara Mutton Recipe | Mutton Rara | Mutton curry | Rara Mutton Bhuna | Spice Eats Mutton Rara |Ingredients for Rare Mutton Curry:|(Tsp- Teaspoon; Tbsp- Tablespoon )| |- Mutton Ribs & Chops - 500 gms|- Muton Mince (Keema) - 250 gms.|For marinating the 500 gms ribs & chops: |- Turmeric Powder- 1/2 tsp|- Kashmiri Chilli Powder- 2 tsp|- Coriander Powder- 2 tsp|- Salt- 1 tsp |- Ginger Garlic paste- 1.5 tsp|- Curd- 5-6 tbsp|Tempering:|- Green Cardamom- 6|- Cinnamon -4 |- Cloves- 6|- Black Cardamom- 2|- Black Peppercorns-6-8|- Mace(Javitri)- few petals|Spice Powders:|- Turmeric- 1/2 tsp|- Kashmiri Chilli Powder- 2 tsp|- Red Chilli Powder- 1 tsp|- Coriander powder- 1.5 tsp|- Garam Masala Powder- 3/4 tsp|- Kasuri Methi Powder-1/2 tsp powder|Other ingredients:|- Onions chopped - 300 gms (4 medium)|- Crushed ginger - 1 tbsp|- Crushed garlic- 1 tbsp|- Sliced & roughly crushed green Chillies- 2-3 |- Tomato purÃ©e (readymade or fresh) 3 tbsp|- Ghee- 4-5 tbsp|- Oil- 2 tbsp|- Coriander leaves, chopped- 2 tbsp|Preparation:|- Marinate the ribs & chops with the ingredients specified. Mix and set aside for an hour. |- Chop the onions. Peel and roughly crush the ginger and garlic. |- Also slice the green chillies and roughly crush these. Set aside. |- For the tomato purÃ©e, you can use readymade tomato purÃ©e/paste or blend red tomatoes to give fresh tomato purÃ©e. |- Dry roast the Kasuri Methi and then crush it with your hand. Set aside for use later.|- Also chop the coriander leaves and set aside. |Process:|- Heat a mix of ghee & oil in a curry pan and then add the whole spices. |- Give a stir and then add the crushed ginger, garlic and green chillies. Fry for 1 min and then add the chopped onions. Fry on medium heat for 13 mins till the onions are light brown in colour. |- Now add the minced meat and fry on high heat for 2 mins. Add all the Spice Powders other than GMP & Kasuri Methi, give a mix .Also add 3/4 tsp salt. Fry on medium heat for 5 mins till the keema is browned & oil separates. |- Now add the marinated mutton and fry on high to medium high heat for 5 mins. Continue to bhunno (fry) for another 5 mins on medium low heat. Add the readymade tomato purÃ©e, give a mix and cook on medium low heat for 2-3 mins. |- Add 300 ml water, give a mix and cover & cook on low heat for around 20 mins. |- Now add the Garam Masala Powder & Kasuri Methi powder. Mix and cover and cook on low heat for 7-8 mins (or 6-7 ???) till the meat is tender and the keema gravy coats the mutton pieces and oil separates. |- Garnish with chopped coriander leaves. Mix and simmer for 1-2 mins. Serve hot with Roti or Rumali Roti. |#raramutton #raragosht #muttonrara #raramuttonrecipe #raramuttoncurry #muttonrararecipe #muttoncurry #spiceeats #spiceeatsrecipes #spiceeatsmutton

title: Petani Protes Larangan Ekspor Minyak Goreng: Sawit Bukan Hanya Milik Oligarki, Tapi Juga Petani
description: Presiden Joko Widodo memutuskan untuk melarang ekspor minyak goreng dan bahan bakunya, mulai 28 april nanti. Pelarangan itu dilakukan agar pasokan minyak goreng di dalam negeri kembali melimpah dan harganya murah. Namun, harga murah belum didapat, alih-alih kebijakan pukul rata itu justru menuai kritik dari sebagian kalangan, yang mempertanyakan nasib lebih dari 30 juta ton crude palm oil akan dikemanakan. Sementara kebutuhan dalam negeri hanya 6-7 juta ton. Lantas efektifkah kebijakan pelarangan ekspor Jokowi ini?|Kebijakan pukul rata larangan ekspor minyak goreng dan bahan bakunya menuai kritik. Sebagian kalangan mempertanyakan nasib lebih dari 30 juta ton produksi crude palm oil akan dikemanakan. Sementara kebutuhan dalam negeri hanya 6-7 juta ton. Lantas efektifkah kebijakan pelarangan ekspor Jokowi untuk mengatasi persoalan kelangkaan dan tingginya harga minyak goreng?|Eva Yunizar membahasnya dalam dialog wawancara via zoom bersama Andre Rosiade selaku Anggota Komisi VI DPR RI F-Partai Gerindra, Bhima Yudhistira selaku Direktur CELIOS dan Petani Sawit, Wayan Supadno.

title: Global National: April 23, 2022 | Mixed messages emerge from front lines in Ukraine
description: Ukrainian President Zelenskyy spoke in person to hundreds of journalists in an underground train station in Kyiv. The president answered questions for more than an hour as Russia continued to pound the front lines. And as western leaders try to re-start negotiations, mixed messages from the front lines are emerging. Mike Drolet has more.| |An early and furious start to the U.S. wildfire season: At least 11 million Americans are under a red flag warning to be extremely careful as fast-moving fires sweep through Arizona, New Mexico and Colorado. Evacuation orders have been issued for several counties as firefighters battle flames fueled by extreme winds. Jennifer Johnson has the latest.| |The Conservative leadership race hit a key benchmark this week. At least eight candidates made the deadline to file the paperwork and submit the first installment of the $300,000 entry fee they need to pay by the end of the month in order to stay in the race. On the West Block, David Akin is joined by two leading lights in Canadaâ€™s Conservative movement, former Saskatchewan premier Brad Wall and former cabinet minister James Moore to examine the health of this race - and the health of the party. | |A battle is brewing in Quebec over a proposed language law that could force college students to take three core courses in French. Anglophone groups say Bill 96 would make many students fail and potentially drive many out of the province. Dan Spector looks at the growing push-back as the legislation nears adoption. | |The job market in Canada is red-hot right now and itâ€™s causing a power shift. There are about a million openings across the country and just about the same number of people looking for jobs. Companies are now being forced to offer more than just a paycheque to attract workers. Anne Gaviola has more. | |Alberta is leading the world in a program that gets surgery patients back on their feet faster. Along with reducing hospitalization time, experts say the program could also cut costs and pain medication use for patients. Su-Ling-Goh reports.| |A thrift store in British Columbia is making a name for itself. Not necessarily for what it sells, but how itâ€™s helping the community it relies on. In just four years the owner of Dannyâ€™s Dynamite Deals has donated tens of thousands of dollars to local schools and charities. title: Xander Schauffele & Patrick Cantlay shoot 12-under 60 | Round 3 | Zurich Classic | 2022
description: In third round Fourball at the 2022 Zurich Classic of New Orleans, Xander Schauffele and Patrick Cantlay fired a 12-under, bogey-free 60 to get to 29-under par through 54 holes. Cantlay and Schauffele have a five-shot lead heading into Sunday.|SUBSCRIBE to PGA TOUR now: http://pgat.us/vBxcZSh||||Returning for its fifth year as a team event, the Zurich Classic of New Orleans will see 80 two-man teams tee it up at TPC Louisiana. The pairings will play best ball on Thursday and Saturday, and alternate shots Friday and Sunday. 2021â€™s Australian winners, Marc Leishman and Cameron Smith will team up once again in the hope of defending their title. Fresh from victory at Augusta, Scottie Scheffler combines with fellow Texan Ryan Palmer, who has pedigree at Zurich, having won the 2019 event alongside Spainâ€™s Jon Rahm. Viktor Hovland and Collin Morikawa make up what looks to be a formidable pairing, while Patrick Cantlay and Xander Schauffele will recreate the Ryder Cup pairing that saw them go undefeated at Whistling Straits in September. ||||Welcome to the official YouTube channel of the PGA TOUR. title: PBS News Weekend full episode, April 23, 2022
description: Saturday on PBS NewsHour Weekend, Russians continue their attack on Ukraine, focusing in on Mariupol. Ukrainian President Volodymyr Zelenskyy announced that Secretary of State Blinken and Defense Secretary Lloyd Austin would meet with him Sunday in Kyiv. Then, we take a look at how very few mask mandates remain in the U.S. as COVID vaccines are still unavailable for the youngest children. title: Why There's No Red iPhone 13 Pro
description: Apple is known for their world class industrial design. So when they decide to use color in a product, they tend to do it well. And nowhere is this more evident than on the iPhone. The gold 5s, rose gold 6s, and midnight green 11 started new design trends that rippled through the tech industry. But one color in particular has stuck around; Product Red. It debuted with the second generation iPod nano in 2006. And has been used on several iPhone models since then. But mysteriously, the color has never been used on a pro model. title: HIGHLIGHTS | Arsenal vs Manchester United (3-1) | Premier League | Tavares, Saka, Xhaka-boom!
description: We moved back into the top four thanks to a pulsating victory over Manchester United.|It was a highly charged, incident-packed encounter from start to finish. Nuno Tavares and Bukayo Saka fired us into a two-goal lead inside half an hour, before United rallied to halve the deficit through Cristiano Ronaldo.|Bruno Fernandes then missed a penalty before Granit Xhaka sealed the points with a superb 25-yard drive. |These lunchtime kick offs can often have a sedate atmosphere early on. Not this one. The crowd were up for it from the kick off, and the team responded immediately.|There were just two minutes on the clock when Tavares gave us the lead. Xhakaâ€™s deep cross was missed by everyone in the United defence and found its way though to Saka. His shot was parried by David de Gea but Tavares was in the right place at the far post to tuck home.|It was the full backâ€™s first goal for the club since joining from Benfica last summer.|United came back. Anthony Elanga had a low shot well saved by Aaron Ramsdale before Gabriel put in a great block after Ramsdale had presented the ball to Fernandes.|Diogo Dalot was next to go close for the visitors, curling a shot from 20 yards over the keeper and against the crossbar.|Chances were coming at both ends, and Eddie Nketiah had a great chance after being slid through on goal by Martin Odegaard but his shot was straight at de Gea.|Moments later Nketiah thought he had beaten the keeper, only for the goal to be ruled out by VAR for a very close offside call. However there was a foul on Saka in the build up, and a spot kick was awarded instead.|For the second time in a week the England man stepped up and netted from the penalty spot.|The two-goal advantage didnâ€™t last long. United had been a threat throughout the opening half hour, and pulled a goal back through Cristiano Ronaldo, who stole in at the far post to fire home a looping cross. Ramsdaleâ€™s moment of hesitation proved costly.|The first half was action-packed, and had flown by. Odegaard had another shot tipped away in injury-time â€“ one of six attempts on target in the opening 45 minutes for us.|Tavares should have hit the target soon after the interval. He found space inside the box, beat his man superbly, but blazed a shot high and wide.|Tavaresâ€™s eventful afternoon continued when he gave away a penalty for handball. Fernandes stepped up, but his shot hit the post and went behind for a goal kick.|It was a big let off, and moments later there was another when Ronaldoâ€™s goal was ruled out for offside by the barest of margins.|Ramsdale came up with a huge save at his near post to turn Dalotâ€™s shot onto the woodwork.|We were living dangerously, but Granit Xhakaâ€™s fierce drive relieved the pressure.|He picked up the ball five yards outside the box, shifted it on to his trusty left foot, and arrowed his shot beyond the despairing de Gea just inside the post.|The Emirates erupted. With the two-goal cushion restored, we closed out the game to earn a second big win in the space of four days.|Teams: |Arsenal: Ramsdale, Cedric, White, Gabriel, Tavares; Elneny, Xhaka;, Saka, Odegaard, Smith Rowe,  Nketiah.|Substitutes: Leno, Tomiyasu, Holding, Lokonga, Azeez, Swanson, Pepe, Martinelli, Lacazette|Manchester United: De Gea, Dalot, Lindelof, Varane, Alex Telles,  McTominay, Matic,  Elanga, Fernandes, Sancho, Ronaldo.|Substitutes  Henderson, Wan-Bissaka, Bailly, Jones, Maguire, Mata, Lingard, Rashford, Garnacho.|#arsenal #bukayosaka #granitxhaka |It puts us six points ahead of United, with five games remaining.Enjoy match highlights, training and behind the scenes to get closer to the likes of Bukayo Saka, Emile Smith Rowe, Vivianne Miedema, Nicolas Pepe, Alexandre Lacazette, Leah Williamson, Bernd Leno, Nikita Parris, Tobin Heath, Mana Iwabuchi, Jordan Nobbs, Takehiro Tomiyasu, Kim Little, Gabriel Martinelli, Aaron Ramsdale, Beth Mead, Ben White, Thomas Partey and more.|Subscribe to the Official Arsenal YouTube Channel: https://arsn.al/youtube|Follow us on Facebook: https://arsn.al/facebook|Follow us on Twitter: https://arsn.al/twitter|Follow us on Instagram: https://arsn.al/instagram|Follow us on TikTok: https://arsn.al/tiktok|This is the Official YouTube channel for Arsenal Football Club.|For more match action, highlights and training videos, make sure you become a digital member and sign up to Arsenal Player. title: Penggeledahan 10 Lokasi Dugaan Korupsi Minyak Goreng, Kejaksaan Agung Sita 650 Dokumen
description: JAKARTA, KOMPAS.TV - Kejaksaan Agung menggeledah 10 lokasi dalam kasus dugaan korupsi dalam pemberian izin fasilitas ekspor minyak sawit mentah, atau CPO.||||Dari sepuluh lokasi, penggeledahan salah satunya dilakukan di rumah Dirjen Perdagangan Luar Negeri Kementerian Perdagangan, Indrasari Wisnu Wardhana yang telah ditetapkan sebagai tersangka.||||Baca Juga Kejagung Ungkap Peran Dirjen Kemendag Soal Korupsi Minyak Goreng di https://www.kompas.tv/article/282507/kejagung-ungkap-peran-dirjen-kemendag-soal-korupsi-minyak-goreng||||Penggeledahan dilakukan pada Selasa (05/04) lalu.||||Tak hanya rumah Dirjen Kemendag, Kejaksaan Agung juga menggeledah kantor Kementerian Perdagangan di Jakarta.||||Dari penggeledahan, Kejagung menyita 650 dokumen serta barang bukti elektronik.||||Barang bukti elektronik ini kini tengah didalami penyidik, untuk mencari tahu secara rinci percakapan para tersangka sehingga berakibat pada perbuatan melawan hukum.||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/282829/penggeledahan-10-lokasi-dugaan-korupsi-minyak-goreng-kejaksaan-agung-sita-650-dokumen

title: Russia Ukraine conflict: Odesa hit by missile attacks
description: Russian forces have been pushing on with their military campaign across the Donbas in eastern Ukraine, and also in the south of the country.|(Subscribe: https://bit.ly/C4_News_Subscribe) |Today another effort to evacuate civilians from the besieged city of Mariupol has again ended in failure.| |The Russian military has been pounding cities in the Luhansk region in the Donbas according to the governor there - forcing Ukrainian troops to pull back in some areas as well as partially blockading Kharkiv in the north east.| |According to the Ukrainian government, Russian forces have also resumed airstrikes over Mariupol in the south and are trying to storm the Azovstal steel works where the remaining Ukrainian soldiers are holding out.  | |And the southern city of Odesa has also been hit in a missile strike.| -----------------------  |Follow us on Instagram - https://www.instagram.com/Channel4News

title: The key to Max's F1 Imola sprint win by Peter Windsor
description: The Saturday sprint F1 race at Imola  looked to be another demonstration of unabashed superiority by Charles Leclerc and Ferrari...until the right-front Pirelli on the F1-75 began to grain and thus to lose grip. Then Max Verstappen, the tyres on his Red Bull RB18 working perfectly, closed in for the kill. In this video, at 06:20, Peter Windsor offers a suggestion as to why there was such a difference in late-race tyre performance between the two cars. Calling on data from FP2 at Imola this morning, Peter also looks ahead to the Emilia Romagna Grand Prix at Imola on Sunday, when the protagonists will also be using harder Pirelli compounds. (Even so, the soft tyre still looks to be very raceable off the line, even with a higher fuel load.)  Peter also analyses another disappointing day for Mercedes; a strong result for McLaren-Mercedes and Alfa Romeo; and the impressive drive by Haas' Mick Schumacher.|With thanks to Jetcraft, the world's largest buyer and seller of executive jets, for their support of this channel|https://jetcraft.com|Follow Peter @peterdwindsor|Images: AMG Mercedes, Red Bull, Alfa Romeo, Scuderia Ferrari, McLaren F1 and Haas|With thanks to Alpinestars|https: alpinestars.com|This channel supports the Race Against Dementia:|https://raceagainstdementia.com|#STANDWITHUKRAINE

title: India breaks Pak's record: 78,000 wave national flag together in Bihar I Watch
description: More than 78,000 Indians simultaneously waved the national flag at the Jagdishpur town in Bihar's Bhojpur district on Saturday, breaking a record that was set by Pakistan 18 years ago when 56,000 Pakistanis waved their national flag at an event in Lahore. The Indian national flag was waved at Jagdishpur for a full five minutes on the occasion of 164th death anniversary of Veer Kunwar Singh, the then king of Jagdishpur who is regarded as one of the heroes of the First War of Independence in 1857. This event was organised as a part of the Union government's 'Azadi Ka Amrit Mahotsav' initiative. title: Ukraine war update: How is Russia doing & what does Ukraine need? | DW News
description: US satellite images appear to show another mass grave in a cemetery east of Mariupol. Pictures taken in late March and mid April suggest fresh parallel trenches were dug. Ukraine has accused Russia of trying to hide evidence of war crimes during the assault on the city. Russia denies the claims.|Ukraine's Azov Regiment has released a video of civilians sheltering in bunkers beneath the Azovstal steel plant in Mariupol. It's not clear when or where the video was filmed. Russian president Vladimir Putin ordered his forces not to storm the plant earlier this week but Ukraine says attacks in the area have continued.|United Nations Secretary-General Antonio Guterres is set to visit Moscow on Tuesday to meet Russian President Vladimir Putin. He'll then head to Ukraine for talks with President Volodymyr Zelenskyy. Guterres will discuss steps to bring about peace following Russia's invasion of Ukraine.|Russia has confirmed the death of one of the crew members of its flagship missile cruiser Moskva, a week after it sank in the Black Sea. The Ministry of Defense said nearly 400 crew members were evacuated. Kremlin critics suspect a much higher number of dead and missing, saying the ship's crew was about 500 strong.|A court in Moscow has ordered opposition activist Vladimir Kara-Murza to remain in pre-trial detention. He's accused of spreading fake news about Russia's army after denouncing the war. Kara-Murza has long been a critic of the Kremlin, and has survived two poison attacks. Human rights groups have called for his release.|Ukraine has warned that Russia plans to attack more countries and expand its war. President Volodymyr Zelenskyy said Ukraine's neighbour Moldova should be concerned about Russia's latest military strategy. |Moldova is home to Trans-nistria, which is a breakaway pro-Russian region which borders Ukraine. Russia is in control of Ukraine's south-east regions, seen here in blue. title: MOON KNIGHT: Who's Inside the Sarcophagus? - THIRD IDENTITY and Twist Ending Explained
description: Moon Knight Episode 4 gave us a lot to talk about. Is Marc in an asylum? Has everything been in his head? Is he dead? Who is Hippo Lady? But for us the biggest question is, who is inside the sarcophagus? It's probably the third personality that's been teased throughout the show. But it could also be Khonshu, an animated character, or Kevin Feige himself. We've got a lot of fun theories, and I promise you one of them is going to be right.|If you're new, Subscribe! â†’ http://bit.ly/subscribe-screencrush|Go here â†’ http://screencrush.com/|Like us â†’ https://www.facebook.com/ScreenCrush|Follow us â†’ https://twitter.com/screencrushnews|Get our newsletter â†’ http://screencrush.com/newsletter/|Written and Hosted by Ryan Arey (http://twitter.com/ryanarey)|Edited by Harriet Lengel-Enright and Randolf Nombrado|#MoonKnight #Sarcophagus #ThirdMan|The ending of episode 4 of Moon Knight upended the entire show. Was the whole series in Marcâ€™s mind? Is the asylum in Marc's mind? Weâ€™ve already put out a couple videos, plus our ending explained, exploring those options. But now I want to hone in on one specific detail about the finale. Who is in this sarcophagus?|There are a couple obvious answers, but we have a few theories that might surprise you. And I have one theory that is very off the wall, but Iâ€™m praying to Khonshu that it's true. Seriously it would be the coolest, weirdest twist in any Marvel show. |First, I think one thing about this ending is clear. Even if the asylum is real, then portions of this ending are happening in Marc's mind. He cannot physically meet Steven in the real world. So, even if he really is in an institution, he is at least hallucinating Steven. So, we can reasonably assume that the other sarcophagus is also in his mind.|Unless, like, the hot new thing for treating the mentally is placing them standing up in sarcophagiâ€”but I doubt it.|So whoever is in this thing was either manifested by Marcâ€“or itâ€™s something that has infiltrated Marcâ€™s mind.|Letâ€™s talk about the most obvious answer for who is inside this thing, before we get to the freaky theories. [more like a freaky circle] This is Marcâ€™s third personality. In the comics, he adopts two alter egos, playboy billionaire philanthropist filmmaker Steven Grant. In the show, they reinvented him as a hapless, sweet gift shoppist.|But in the comics, the other alter ego is Jake Lockley, a mustachioed cab driver who gathers info from the streets. Now later issues of Moon Knight made it clear that these alter egos were actual alter personalities, and Marc had dissociative identity disorder since he was a child.|Steven was Marcâ€™s childhood best friend, and Jake became more of a protector personality. There was always something darker about Jakeâ€“he was a little more prone to violence.|Now, in this show we have seen numerous hints that Mars has more than 2 identities. Some of these hints were obvious, like when neither of them remember going on a killing spree [what did you do/not me].|But other hints were more subtleâ€“like why would Marc make a date with this woman? [best steak in town]. Sheâ€™s pretty, but Marc is laser focused on his mission, and living near his ex-wife, who heâ€™s hiding from. He wouldnâ€™t risk running into her at a steak joint. Itâ€™s obviously a third personality that lives Stevenâ€™s life better than him.|There are even indications that this third personality took over during the fight for the scarab. Remember, Steven wakes up with his jaw out of place. So it took one hell of a fall to knock Marc out. Maybe, in Germany, he stays knocked out, and itâ€™s the brutal violent Jake Lockley who killed these people. |Thereâ€™s another strange indication of Jake leading Stevenâ€™s life, in the fourth episode. Just before heâ€™s supposed to belay down, this happens.Thatâ€™s the same sound as when he switches bodies before [clip]. And he appears to punch himself in the jaw. Maybe this was the third personality breaking out, then punching Steven so he can take over the body. |There are other hints that Jake is in the show, like triple mirrors, and 3 Oscar Isaacs in the credits. This sarcophagus is also blood red, indicating a violent personality. Itâ€™s also standing up, while Stevenâ€™s was lying down. This indicates that Stevem is passive, at restâ€“while this altar is violent and ready to spring into action. |Also, this figure on the sarcophagus looks like a ba-bird. This is a very interesting addition. The ba-bird was an aspect of the mummified personâ€™s soul. It was able to travel out of the tomb to the outside world, but always had to return to the body.|It is interesting if this is Jake. Because, Jake is trapped inside this tomb most of the time, or trapped inside Marcâ€™s mind. But his ba, the spirit, is able to occasionally venture into the outside world, do some murderinâ€™, before it has to return to the tomb.

title: J&K: PM Modi to inaugurate Banihal-Qazigund tunnel; How it will boost connectivity
description: PM Modi who will be on J&K visit on Sunday will inaugurate the Banihal-Qazigund Road Tunnel, built at a cost of over Rs 3,100 crore. The 8.45 km long tunnel would reduce the road distance between Banihal and Qazigund by 16 km, and reduce journey time by around one and a half hour. The tunnel would help establish an all weather connection between Jammu and Kashmir, and bring the two regions closer. On Sunday, all eyes will be on PM Modi who will inaugurating this tunnel. title: Ultimate Bangladeshi Food!! GIANT BEEF MEZBAN in Chittagong, Bangladesh!!
description: ğŸ¥ Watch - Unique Village Food Bangladesh: https://youtu.be/BMhdzxNR3ps|ğŸ‡§ğŸ‡© Huge thanks to @Petuk Couple |ğŸ”” SUBSCRIBE: http://bit.ly/MarkWiensSubscribe Donâ€™t miss new food videos!|CHITTAGONG, BANGLADESH - Welcome to Chittagong in the south of Bangladesh, along the coast, is famous for its mezban - a traditional meal celebration where a full cow is cooked into 4 different dishes. Today we have the extremely special opportunity to see the dishes of a mezban being  prepared and to watch the entire process.|Mezzan Haile Ayun (https://goo.gl/maps/TBKPjdYTHNudh4nL9) is a restaurant in Chittagong with locations in Dhaka and Sharjah that specializes in mezban. We had the privilege to go to their central kitchen to watch the entire process. Every mezban meal starts with an entire cow - the full cow. The meat must be fresh and they parted it out within 45 minutes, all the way from cow to cubes.|The most important dish is the mezbani beef, a curry, but like a slow cooked stew filled with beef, a huge amount of spices, green chilies, mustard oil, and one of the signature tastes from a spice called radhuni. Every dish cooks over fire, slow cooked until fully mingled and flavors melting together. Additionally thereâ€™s black beef cooked in spices and dry fried until all the spices were caked onto each cube meat. Another dish is the daal, which is cooked with all the organs of the cow. And finally the bones which are cooked for the flavor, bone marrow, in a soup. The entire meal, all four dishes are a traditional Bangladeshi mezban.|The meal was outstanding, so much flavor so fresh, and so complex. All the dishes each went together in perfect harmony. Itâ€™s one of the best food experiences in Bangladesh and it was truly memorable.|Thank you so much to Petuk Couple (https://www.youtube.com/c/PetukCouple) for arranging this and for showing me around Bangladesh!|ğŸ“Mezzan Haile Ayun: https://goo.gl/maps/TBKPjdYTHNudh4nL9|ğŸµMUSIC: |https://goo.gl/HwVjdo|â€”â€”â€”â€”â€”â€”â€”â€”â€”â€”â€”â€”â€”â€”â€”â€”â€”â€”|ğŸ‘•Get t-shirts and caps:|https://migrationology.com/store/|â€”â€”â€”â€”â€”â€”â€”â€”â€”â€”â€”â€”â€”â€”â€”â€”â€”â€”|ğŸ“±FOLLOW:|Instagram: https://instagram.com/migrationology|Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/migrationology
